INSTALL

To install this plugin, copy his directory into the 'plugins' directory
of your roundcube instance and activate the plugin name by adding his name
'vacation' to the option array 'plugins' in config/main.inc.php :

	// List of active plugins (in plugins/ directory)
	$rcmail_config['plugins'] = array('vacation');

Edit now the plugin configuration file 'config.inc.php'. You must choose the
driver for your backend storage and configure his options. For more information,
please take a look in the directory /doc.
